{"tid":1423014,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] IT人進場時間到了","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T05:17:45.000Z","uid":174070,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"efb0b843517ea847c4718025b566b1c633cd7cbc","tid":1423014,"uid":174070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:38:18.000Z","msg":"Sorry 我本身係一個IT人，真係唔識起Title<br />\n我係一個土生土長嘅香港人，今年都31喇<br />\n<br />\n今日碌碌下連登，比下面#259位巴打創發咗我<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1421898/page/11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1421898/page/11</a><br />\n<br />\n我無發夢去前線，無做過乜，因為我嘅無力感好重，真係唔覺得有可能動搖到香港政府<br />\n但琴日見一位巴打開post話要搞民間記者會，到今日11點真係開到出來⋯⋯<br />\n小弟真係有D內疚，好大感觸⋯⋯<br />\n<strong>「我頂你個肺吖，有時D嘢真係講講下就做到出來⋯⋯」</strong><br />\n以往幾年我工餘時間都真係有唸過要點寫D爆app出來⋯⋯無奈地每一次都係衰收尾<br />\n<strong>無勇氣去推出街，成日都左計右計，又驚無人用，又驚要比server錢會蝕，點返本呀？</strong><br />\n<br />\n到今日呢個idea，我又唸到，不如真係寫隻app喇？<br />\n既然我地偉大嘅林鄭月娥特首話會每日搞記者會呀嘛？即係代表佢準備好打長期戰啦？<br />\n咁我係咪可以寫隻app去令個抗爭動作sustainable呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果你問我驚唔驚被秋後算帳？sorry，我本人真係唔驚 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但我真係會擔心我家人受影響</span><br />\n我嘅出發點係集民意，同埋提供一個平台比受影響嘅人知道時間表，佢地可以避免受影響<br />\n<br />\n廢話唔再多講，我用咗一個車程去唸開唔開post，再用一個沖涼時間去唸隻app可以點發展：<br />\nPreparation:<br />\n1. 先用我本人名義係App Store同Play Store開developer account<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">Android已有, iOS交續費就ok</span></em><br />\n2. 有覺悟<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">未好肯定有，聽日睇下個post係正皮多定負皮多</span></em><br />\n<br />\nPhase 1 App功能：<br />\n1. 主頁放抗爭時間表（每日update 1次, 暫時可能只係一張圖）<br />\n2. Bingo表（為今次抗爭活動帶來一點歡樂，但可能會有人覺得我抽水／膠化運動，咁就要睇返聽日個正負皮比例，有民意先會真係做出來）<br />\n因為真係唔想個運動持續太耐（太耐即係全香港人keep住輸）<br />\n暫時第一步唔會唸起個server，大約會放哂source code上GitHub，然後用GitHub upload抗爭時間表. 大數據方面只會用Google analytics<br />\n大約需時2個man day<br />\n<br />\n真係成事的話，bingo格內的字／格數都交由各連登仔決定（就好似連登女神咁，限時內邊個字最多人投就會選用佢地）<br />\n<br />\nPhase 2 App功能：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你 真係想有Phase 2? 我都想有一日大家都可以除低口罩相認，然後比個hug大家呀</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"43f1417cb9221d18c145feb16d6a8282dd3bf5df","tid":1423014,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:38:39.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"58c1c1d842b0b1a2a8100a28e5773db251c29eae","tid":1423014,"uid":239620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:48:06.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ea05f190ec99a0fd843fa44cc7d78beb50653a","tid":1423014,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:55:13.000Z","msg":"不如求其起住個Wordpress先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa